rows.label: qst501001_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey there.
Looking to transfer some cash?

rows.label: qst501001_msg0002
rows.name: How much you wanna send?

rows.label: qst501001_msg0003
rows.name: Send some money?

rows.label: qst501001_msg0018
rows.name: Send 10,000G

rows.label: qst501001_msg0019
rows.name: Send 30,000G

rows.label: qst501001_msg0020
rows.name: Send 90,000G

rows.label: qst501001_msg0021
rows.name: Don't send anything

rows.label: qst501001_msg0004
rows.name: OK, that all seems to be in order.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0005
rows.name:
You're a good kid, you know.
Always sending money home like this.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0006
rows.name:
It'll be for Correl in Iyasaki Village,
right? Yeah, I still remember.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0007
rows.name:
Don't worry, you can count on me
to get it delivered safe.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0008
rows.name: Whew, that's quite the sum.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0009
rows.name:
Don't worry, we only assign the best
couriers to big transfers like this.
We'll see it gets there safe.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0010
rows.name:
'Course, given how tough you guys
are, it might be easier for you to
just deliver the cash in person...

rows.label: qst501001_msg0011
rows.name:
But hey, I guess I can see how that
might feel awkward sometimes.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0012
rows.name:
Can't complain when you're giving
us work to do!

rows.label: qst501001_msg0013
rows.name: So, how much'll it be this time?

rows.label: qst501001_msg0014
rows.name:
Hey there.
Looking to transfer some cash?

rows.label: qst501001_msg0015
rows.name:
Ah, but listen. You've already sent over
90,000G lately, and that's on top of
the 90 thousand from that big job.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0016
rows.name:
Don't you think you've done enough
for now? I'd go have a chat with that
Correl, if I were you.

rows.label: qst501001_msg0017
rows.name:
If she needs any more than this,
she must be trying to build a castle
or something!
